photo.alt:
A comic of two foxes, one of whom is blue, the other is green. In this one, they are walking, when Blue notices something.
Blue: Hey, it's almost lunchtime.
Green: We have food at home.

Blue turns to Green, who is persuaded.
Blue: We could have that tomorrow.
Green: That's true.

Green heads off to the direction Blue had been looking towards.
Green: Oh no, you talked me into getting takeout again.

Both of the foxes head to the same direction, with no intention to resist the temptation.
Green: Oh no.
Blue: Oh noo.
